{"tid":929111,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"松岡茉優被爆已同居一年","createTime":"2018-12-05T10:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T14:10:38.000Z","uid":221236,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"04fcd3ebba6c9ea56d56d9745f324f3b1ce8d160","tid":929111,"uid":221236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:42:36.000Z","msg":"松岡茉優被爆與Hey！Say！JUMP的27歲成員有岡大貴同居一年<br />\n<br />\n2016年經友人飯局認識有岡，兩人因同樣喜愛漫畫，秘密拍拖近兩年。兩人為免戀情曝光，平日絕不外出拍拖。有岡不時會親自下廚，與女友在家中見面兼歎日本酒。兩人為方便見面，一年前更索性搬到同一幢大廈居住。<br />\n<br />\n大貴你要幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ykOeYJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FykOeYJM.jpg&h=27ec7cfc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cb150dbbd10539901e4c0134798fa915b5dc33a","tid":929111,"uid":102880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96018c328d5826f845997eb2ec2e4f2e91867aa7","tid":929111,"uid":4618,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"那個了唷"},{"pid":"9606d3ede9ae7aa2a9d460579c1edbf405f035e3","tid":929111,"uid":221236,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"96018c328d5826f845997eb2ec2e4f2e91867aa7","tid":929111,"uid":4618,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"那個了唷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:08:25.000Z","msg":"同居冇那個先驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a35fc33aa18b40dc7d652cffb1057b1c7b96bbc","tid":929111,"uid":49197,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:15:59.000Z","msg":"有岡大貴得164cm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a91f7